Did someone say COSTCO EXCLUSIVE? 😱🚨

Yes you heard correctly, we are launching a NEW, Costco Exclusive product in the Northeast and Southeast regions, this week and next! 🥗

Our new PuraVida Foods ‘Fire Roasted Elote Street Corn with Queso Fresco’ is a mix of corn, poblano and red bell peppers, extra virgin olive oil and adobo spices, tossed in a Mexican lime crema AND Queso fresco, finished off with some cilantro 🤤

Do we really need to say more?? This flavourful veggie mix is the perfect side dish for all your summer food-ventures! 🌽

What will you make with this delicious product? 🤔💬

Happy Independence Day! 🥳🇺🇸

We asked Benny Brussels how he’ll be celebrating the 4th of July, and here was his response: 

‘Food, Food, and MORE FOOD! Along with friends and family of course 😋’ 

We couldn’t think of a better way to spend it ourselves, and with so many flame grilled PuraVida Foods options to choose from, your backyard BBQ would not be complete without a side of our veggies 🤤🍖

How are you celebrating this momentous day? 🤔🇺🇸

Is it getting hot in here, or is it just our PuraVida Foods ‘Flame Grilled Adobo Street Corn & Peppers’? 🤔🔥

This blend of sweet corn, red and poblano peppers and adobo Chile seasoning is perfect if you’re looking to add a little kick to your dish 🤤

We love adding them to a plate of nachos or into a salad, but really these are the perfect addition to any meal! 

Can you handle the heat? 🔥

Feeling something simple and delicious? Have some Brussels Sprouts 🥗

Our PuraVida Foods ‘Fire Roasted Brussels Sprouts’ are simply seasoned with Himalayan pink salt and cracked black peppercorn, are fire roasted to perfection in extra virgin olive oil 🔥

Ready in just minutes, they can be enjoyed by themselves or mixed into your favourite stir-fry, pasta, or anything else! 🥢

Are you a Brussels Sprouts fan? (We definitely are)🤔💬
